{"tid":505325,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"聯想抽高逾６％，本周暫累升逾３７％","createTime":"2017-12-21T03:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T07:02:21.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7ae7eecbcf6ebb03dfedda022d2c7c67a9e016","tid":505325,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:59:11.000Z","msg":"聯想控股（３３９６）抽高逾６％，本周暫累升逾３７％<br />\n以更佳效果檢視 &raquo;<br />\n　　《經濟通通訊社２１日專訊》聯想控股（０３３９６）現價上升６﹒２３％，報２９元；成交約５１２萬股，涉資１﹒４２億元，主動買盤６４％。該股本周走勢強勁，以現價計，本周暫累升３７﹒４％。　　聯想集團（００９９２）現價則下跌０﹒２３％，報４﹒３５元；成交約５８７萬股，涉資２５４１萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8561f274d44d91feaccdac8cab226a07c28f2852","tid":505325,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e87f8a41e791604f7eb8dbcaa7418fa5ac548825","tid":505325,"uid":9391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚇撚死仲以為992<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aaf86aa89ee3ae1716f02fddbc6bb985892b89e","tid":505325,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚇撚死仲以為992<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n992母公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6510c324ef8d9b9199f5490bb571faab7f3eab6e","tid":505325,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:12:04.000Z","msg":"聯想控股再度大漲12% 四日累漲45%市值破700億<br />\n<br />\n新浪港股訊 聯想控股股價連續三日走高，三日累計大漲29%，更是創2015年12月以來新高。聯想控股今日股價一度跌近4%，現股價再度大漲，現漲12%，報價30.8港元，截至發稿，近4日累漲45%，市值突破700億港元，最新市值為715億港元。這背後的刺激因素是其投資的一家韓國娛樂公司擬申請IPO，以及市場預期聯想控股可能成為H股全流通試點公司。<br />\n<br />\nH股全流通試點公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dd9f6e30e9bf1aec3